defaultis 
defaultwithin twelve months of the date of a general or local election; and
default(b)
default              
defaultwho retain a “presumption of rehabilitation”; and
default(c)
default              
defaultwho are 
defaultalready 
default“eligible” to vote under the rules;
defaultwill be entitled to vote at that election.
